translation[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,135,Futhi bathi “yibani amaJuda noma amaKristu niyoholwa kepha inkolo ka-Abrahamu iqotho futhi wayengesiyena omunye wabakhonza izithombe”
  2,136,"Bathi “siyakholwa kuMvelinqangi nakulokho okwehliselwe kuthina, futhi nakulokho okwehliselwa ku-Abrahamu naku- Ishmayeli naku-Isaka nakuJakobe nasezizweni, futhi nalokho okwanikwa uMose noJesu nalokho okwanikwa abaphrofethi okuvela eNkosini yabo. Asibandlululi (umphrofethi) ngisho noyedwa phakathi kwabo futhi singabazinikele kuye (uMvelinqangi)"
  2,137,"Ngakho-ke uma bekholwa ngokufanayo nalokho enikholelwa kukona bangabaholiweyo, kepha uma befulathela (imibiko) badala uqhekeko uMvelinqangi uyananela uma nibhekene nabo futhi ungozwayo onolowazi"
  2,138,(Ithi okwethu) inkolo kaMvelinqangi futhi ubani ongcono kunoMvelinqangi ngenkolo futhi siyizikhonzi zakhe
  2,139,"Ithi “ngakube niphikisana nathi ngoMvelinqangi kulapho eyiNkosi yethu futhi eyiNkosi yenu, okwethu yimisebenzi yethu futhi nokwenu yimisebenzi yenu, futhi sizinikele ngokuqotho kuyena"
  2,140,Noma nithi “u-Abrahamu no-Ishmayeli no-Isak noJakobe nezizwe babengamaJuda noma amaKristu na?” Ithi “ngakube yinina enazi kangcono noma uMvelinqangi na?” futhi ubani ongalungile kakhulu kunalowo ofihla ubufakazi obukuye abuthole kuMvelinqangi? Futhi akusho ukuthi uMvelinqangi akakunakile enikwenzayo
  2,141,"Labo-ke yisizwe sasendulo futhi okwabo yilokho abakuzuza, futhi okwenu yilokho enikuzuzile, futhi angeke nibuzwe ngalokho ababekwenza"